data.description: Welcome to this good as new 4 bed, 2.5 bath home in the highly desirable Harris County area. Resting on a gracious 2.02 acres, noteworthy features include an open floor plan, practically new engineered hardwood floors, a large granite countertop kitchen island, stainless steel appliances, and separate dining area. Upstairs, comfort awaits in the generous master suite and master bath, featuring double vanities and a large walk-in closet. Plush STAINMASTER carpet throughout the upstairs area provides durability while adding to the comfort of this exquisite home. Fresh paint throughout and Ecobee smart thermostats. Outdoors, enjoy a covered gameday patio with a wood burning fireplace. Hardware for your outdoor flatscreen tv has already been installed. Enjoy family fun, game/movie nights, or quiet evenings as you sit by the fire. This home won't last long, so schedule your showing today.
